The story continues. Malcolm Macarthur strikes a second time, killing Dónal Dunne, a young farmer, while the Garda desperately tries to solve the case. Gubu is a seven-part podcast series about the Malcolm Macarthur affair. The first two episodes will be published on Saturday, June 4th. The following episodes will be published daily from Monday, June 6th, to Friday, June 10th. Gubu is researched, reported and narrated by Harry McGee and edited by Enda O’Dowd.